title: 373. Q&AF: Is It Too Late To Start?, Comparing Hard Times In Life & Surrounding Yourself With The Right People Ft. Wes Watson
itunes:title: 373. Q&AF: Is It Too Late To Start?, Comparing Hard Times In Life & Surrounding Yourself With The Right People Ft. Wes Watson
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ are joined in the studio by entrepreneur Wes Watson. They answer your questions on what's the best practice for starting a new project as you begin to age, how to overcome the mentality of thinking you have the worst problems in the world, and how to select the right people for your inner circle.
